Speaker 2: Okay. Yeah, unfortunately, I mean, it got delivered from our end.

Speaker 1: So you can go ahead and place another order. Would you like to place another order?

Speaker 2: Yes, and I want you to send it to my post office box.

Speaker 1: To your PO box? Sure.

Speaker 2: Yeah.

Speaker 1: It looks like you got a quantity of 40, 100 milligrams.

Speaker 2: Okay, so it's the same price, okay?

Speaker 1: Yeah, yeah. I just need them. I mean, I was counting on them.

Speaker 1: Oh, okay.

Speaker 1: Correct.

Speaker 2: Yep.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: And can you overnight them to me?

Speaker 1: Okay, so overnight shipping will be an extra $38.

Speaker 2: I don't care.

Speaker 1: Okay, I'm going to add those $38. It will be charged on the same card, okay?

Speaker 2: Correct.

Speaker 1: Great, you're all set, Brian. I was able to successfully place in that order for you.

Speaker 2: So it should be shipping out tomorrow, not today, okay?

Speaker 1: Okay, sounds good. Thank you so much. I'm sorry.

Speaker 2: No worries.

Speaker 1: It just sucks that people steal stuff.

Speaker 2: Yeah, that's horrible. Yes, I know.
